@*这个叫代码块，里面可以是语句，也可以是html元素，语句会被执行，而html元素会被提取出来，渲染到页面上*@
@{
    var stu = new Student()
    {
        Name = "zhangsan",
        Age = 10
    };

    var value = 100;
    value++;

    <p>@(stu.Age)</p>
    stu.Age++;
    <p>@(stu.Age)</p>
}

@*这个叫表达式，它会取完值，ToString之后写入页面，里面必须是变量或者执行方法*@
<div>@(stu.Name)</div>
<div>@(stu.GetResult<int>(stu.Age))</div>



@*下面是各种语句的用法*@

@*1.if语句的使用*@
@if (value % 2 == 0)
{
    <p>The value was even.</p>
}
else if (value >= 1337)
{
    <p>The value is large.</p>
}
else
{
    <p>The value is odd and small.</p>
}

@*2.switch*@
@switch (value)
{
    case 1:
        <p>The value is 1!</p>
        break;
    case 1337:
        <p>Your number is 1337!</p>
        break;
    default:
        <p>Your number wasn't 1 or 1337.</p>
        break;
}

@*3.foreach*@
@{
    var stuList = new List<Student>()
{
new Student()
{
Name="Jack",
Age=12
},
new Student()
{
Name="Marry",
Age=14
}
};
}
@foreach (var student in stuList)
{
    <p>Name: @student.Name</p>
    <p>Age: @student.Age</p>
}

@*4.try catch*@
@try
{
    throw new Exception("This is a test exception");
}
catch (Exception e)
{
    <p>@e.Message</p>
}
finally
{
    <p>finally</p>
}

@*5.定义一个方法，并调用*@
@functions{
    public string GetResult()
    {
        return "This is result";
    }
}
<div>@GetResult()</div>

